content:
Welcome to the TLS Community Server!

This is a comprehensive guide/FAQ for the server! if you need more help, feel free to ask a question in #help!

embeds.title: What's this server for?
embeds.description: This server is for Hanging out, Sharing cool creations and meida, and also for getting updates for TLS's Projects!

embeds.title: What are the channels for TLS's Projects?
embeds.description: The main channels for this will be:

fields.name: #sneak-peaks
fields.value: this channel has  sneak peaks for TLS's upcoming projects!

fields.name: #videos
fields.value: this channel showcases videos made by TLS and will have announcements for when new ones come around!

fields.name: #releases
fields.value: this channel showcases all the finished projects by TLS!

fields.name: #drawings
fields.value: for sharing your drawings, digital or physical!

fields.name: #videos
fields.value: for sharing videos you've made or videos which showcase your art!

fields.name: #coding
fields.value: for asking coding related questions or sharing your cool code!

fields.name: #etc
fields.value: for sharing other projects and creations you've made!

fields.name: #self-promo
fields.value:
this channel is for self promotion, dont feel afraid to send your name in it!
P.S. please do not use other channels for this purpose

embeds.title: Where can i share my own creations?

fields.name: https://discord.com/channels/1228051694492061798/1228052100072603739
fields.value: You can share random song quotes or attempt to coordinate to sing a whole song together!

fields.name: #keyboard-mashing
fields.value: this channel's only reason to exist is to stim happily! mash as you'd like!

fields.name: #counting-channel
fields.value: count as far as you'd like! if someone breaks the loop everyone restarts!

fields.name: #game-screenshots
fields.value: Share screenshots from a game you play!

fields.name: #out-of-context-quotes
fields.value: Quote other server members(with permission of course.)!
